     BF88 0010     
28061 BF8A 1202            byte >12,>02,>2c,>08                                ; 8  - We're being hit by lasers
     BF8C 2C08     
28062 BF8E 1103            byte >11,>03,>f0,>18                                ; 16 - We died 1 / We made a hit or kill 2
     BF90 F018     
